Sentencas: MyCe1-x-yMnxO2- (M=La, Gd) oxides have been investigated as oxygen reduction catalysts for LSM-YSZ based ternary cathodes.
Titulo: Development of Ternary Cathodes Using MyCe1-x-yMnxO2-δ (M=La, Gd) as Catalysts for Oxygen Reduction Reactions

Sentencas: MyCe1-x-yMnxO2- samples are characterized by X-ray diffraction (XRD), temperature programmed reduction of H2 (H2-TPR), and temperature programmed desorption of O2 (O2-TPD).
Titulo: Development of Ternary Cathodes Using MyCe1-x-yMnxO2-δ (M=La, Gd) as Catalysts for Oxygen Reduction Reactions

Sentencas: The results show that the incorporation of M (M=La, Gd) ions increases the solution limit of Mn in the solid solutions, which increases the amount of oxygen vacancies and promotes oxygen adsorption and dissociation processes.
Titulo: Development of Ternary Cathodes Using MyCe1-x-yMnxO2-δ (M=La, Gd) as Catalysts for Oxygen Reduction Reactions

Sentencas: The ternary cathodes show much higher electrochemical performance than LSM-YSZ binary cathode, and greatly accelerate oxygen dissociative adsorption and diffusion of oxygen species.
Titulo: Development of Ternary Cathodes Using MyCe1-x-yMnxO2-δ (M=La, Gd) as Catalysts for Oxygen Reduction Reactions

Sentencas: The MyCe1-x-yMnxO2- catalysts exhibit greatly high activity for oxygen reduction at intermediate temperature.
Titulo: Development of Ternary Cathodes Using MyCe1-x-yMnxO2-δ (M=La, Gd) as Catalysts for Oxygen Reduction Reactions

Sentencas: The ternary cathodes have high stability and high resistance to CO2 at 600 degrees C.
Titulo: Development of Ternary Cathodes Using MyCe1-x-yMnxO2-δ (M=La, Gd) as Catalysts for Oxygen Reduction Reactions
